Im not sure exactly how they work, but the encryption that is used
in the uk sky satellite network _has_ ben broken, and cards are
available to decrypt the sky signals. The cards are known as 'Ho
Lee Fook' cards, and for abour 175usd, you can watch unlimited,
perfectly decryped tv. 

